{"tid":2192594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"花木蘭不就是古代川島芳子","createTime":"2020-09-07T08:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T10:06:45.000Z","uid":261647,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c34ba4a7e228bdd81e1a1035d42807bc125a0711","tid":2192594,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:25:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158544591622357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10158544591622357&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp5NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=60a2e832\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158544591622357</a><br />\n<br />\n花木蘭不就是古代川島芳子，一樣是侵略漢人的外族，一樣是女扮男裝，一樣是死了之後被人當成漢人。"},{"pid":"cea3723b8811c947518e3006f198874c238234f1","tid":2192594,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:55:12.000Z","msg":"但花木蘭冇自稱係中國人"},{"pid":"10a089fabaa9ed780438cdce105280ab29771c0c","tid":2192594,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cea3723b8811c947518e3006f198874c238234f1","tid":2192594,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:55:12.000Z","msg":"但花木蘭冇自稱係中國人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:58:34.000Z","msg":"川島芳子係滿洲人<br />\n但判佢漢奸罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd898c6f2a4581765933c7b4393431d58fa1d53","tid":2192594,"uid":249094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10a089fabaa9ed780438cdce105280ab29771c0c","tid":2192594,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cea3723b8811c947518e3006f198874c238234f1","tid":2192594,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:55:12.000Z","msg":"但花木蘭冇自稱係中國人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:58:34.000Z","msg":"川島芳子係滿洲人<br />\n但判佢漢奸罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:01:04.000Z","msg":"